## Creating an agent

```python
from langchain.agents import create_agent

agent = create_agent(
    model=llm,
    tools=[...],
    system_prompt="...",
    checkpointer=checkpointer,
    middleware=[...],
)
```

## Initialising the model

```python
from langchain_openai import ChatOpenAI

llm = ChatOpenAI(
    model="gpt-4o-mini",
    temperature=0.2,
    openai_api_key="sk-...",   # always pass explicitly
)
```

## Defining tools

```python
def my_tool(param: str) -> str:
    """One-line description — this becomes the tool's schema."""
    ...

agent = create_agent(model=llm, tools=[my_tool])
```


## Structured output

```python
from pydantic import BaseModel

class MyResponse(BaseModel):
    answer: str

agent = create_agent(model=llm, response_format=MyResponse)
```

