## Deprecated — never use these

| ❌ Forbidden | ✅ Replacement |
|---|---|
| `initialize_agent` | `create_agent` |
| `AgentExecutor` | `create_agent` |
| `create_react_agent` (raw langgraph) | `create_agent` |
| `LLMChain` | `create_agent` or `llm.invoke` |
| `llm.predict` | `llm.invoke` |
| `ConversationBufferMemory` | LangGraph checkpointer |
| `from langchain.memory import ...` | LangGraph checkpointer |
